#    include/  → *.h headers
#    src/      → *.cpp sources
#    CMakeLists.txt | README.md | WINDOWS_SETUP.md
#    generate_test_pcap.py
# ============================================================


# ============================================================
# ALWAYS KEEP — never ignore these source files
# ============================================================
